  slug = "decision-records"
  description = "Elevate Architecture Decision Records (ADRs) from unstructured doc artifacts to structured first-class artifacts with: context (why the decision was needed), options considered (with trade-offs for each), decision (the chosen path with rationale), consequences (what follows from the choice), and supersedes/superseded-by links. Rejected alternatives are preserved as negative space. ADRs bridge solution framing (Manifesto 3.2) and knowledge capture (Manifesto 5.2) — they answer 'why' when the code only shows 'what'."

